<exercise id="fs-id1163752803784">
<problem id="fs-id1163755409244">
<para id="fs-id1163757217403">What are the advantages and disadvantages of having so many levels of subnational governments in the United States? Explain.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1163755113320">
<problem id="fs-id1163755069416">
<para id="fs-id1163757471130">In which level of substate government would you be most likely to get involved? Why?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1163755472346">
<problem id="fs-id1163757522869">
<para id="fs-id1163757480997">Is it preferable for representatives in the state legislature to behave as trustees or as delegates? Why?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1163755382493">
<problem id="fs-id1163757217786">
<para id="fs-id1163757367396">Do term limits seem to have more advantages or disadvantages? Defend your answer.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
</section>
